narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I took this class as a senior requirement. If you take this class, make sure to select your supervisor wisely.
This may sound obvious, but it is what you make it to be.
I would recommend this class to another mechanical engineering major because I think it is a really good experience to do individual research

MENG 472 is the senior project course. You will get out what you put in, but expect to put in a significant amount of time. Choose an adviser that fits your project and your style of work. The assignments are a project outline at the beginning, a midyear report (5 pages), a final report (15 pages), and a final presentation (15 minutes).
